### Component

Forge

### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?

- [X] Foundry
- [X] Foundryup

### What version of Foundry are you on?

latest

### What command(s) is the bug in?

script

### Operating System

macOS (Apple Silicon)

### Describe the bug

Given contract and script :
```solidity
// SPDX-License-Identifier: UNLICENSED
pragma solidity ^0.8.13;

contract SampleContract {
    uint256 public counter;

    function increase() public {
        counter++;
    }
}

```

```solidity
// SPDX-License-Identifier: UNLICENSED
pragma solidity ^0.8.13;

import "forge-std/Script.sol";
import "../src/SampleContract.sol";

contract ContractScript is Script {
    function setUp() public {}

    function run() public {
        vm.broadcast();

        SampleContract sampleContract = new SampleContract();
        sampleContract.increase();

        vm.stopBroadcast();        
    }
}
```

After executing the script with:
```
forge script script/Contract.s.sol:ContractScript --rpc-url http://127.0.0.1:8545 --private-key... --broadcast
```

Run file looks like this:

