Shouldn't this file contain a `increase()` tx in a traction list? As far as I can tell, this function wasn't executed at all ie.:

```sh
cast call 0x5fbdb2315678afecb367f032d93f642f64180aa3 "counter()(uint256)" --rpc-url http://127.0.0.1:8545
```

If this is really a bug, I can try submitting a PR.
